e="pdf" xlink:href="acem0022-0299-sd1.pdf" xlink:type="simple" id="d35e1711" position="anchor"/></supplementary-material><supplementary-material content-type="local-data" id="sd2"><caption><p><bold>Data Supplement S2.</bold> Any adverse outcomes from the EINSTEIN PE study in relation to simplified Pulmonary Embolism Severity Index score and time period: (A) &#x02264;7&#x000a0;days; (B) &#x02264;14&#x000a0;days; (C) &#x02264;30&#x000a0;days; (D) &#x02264;90&#x000a0;days; and (E) full treatment period.</p></caption><media mimetype="pdf" mime-subtype="pdf" xlink:href="acem0022-0299-sd2.pdf" xlink:type="simple" id="d35e1718" position="anchor"/></supplementary-material></sec></back></article>